{"tid":940674,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"後生仔吹水活動group招人啦！！！","createTime":"2018-12-14T06:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T08:09:47.000Z","uid":76587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3497867ac69215be04d02b7f28ccbca5a77d937a","tid":940674,"uid":76587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:23:38.000Z","msg":"最近有冇心事想揾人傾下但冇地方？<br />\n有冇啲開心搞笑嘢想同人講但又唔知揾邊個？<br />\n如果有，咁就啱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後生仔吹水活動group招人啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n我哋定期會搞活動俾大家一齊開開心心玩下~~<br />\n無論係行山睇戲食飯 定 溜冰踩單車，只要你出聲，就會有人陪你<br />\n我地Group的原意係想整一個人少少的group<br />\n比大家Close d傾下計交下心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你有心事想搵人傾，有咩生活的難題<br />\n都歡迎係group講 我地希望個group就好似一個大家庭咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除左一般搞下飯局飲下野之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地會搞下唔同的活動 <br />\n例如睇戲、舞台劇、音樂會、行山、踩單車<br />\n有興趣又夾啱時間隨時拉大隊參加<br />\n大家可以隨時自由建議 <br />\n<br />\n我地target大約係90後的朋友仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中學生就可能唔太適合了 <br />\n我地盡量唔會令到男女比例失衡 <br />\n唔洗擔心 <br />\n<br />\n新人絕對唔洗怕小圈子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喱個新group少過10個人<br />\n我地會主動關心你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你想舊人自介 <br />\n我地都會介紹自己<br />\n<br />\n好啦 講左好多廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n快d填表入group！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfu-KZEnY0rBxEYz1P4uYW-dLuXyOPPd-9O57LG5lmx7ee_QQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfu-KZEnY0rBxEYz1P4uYW-dLuXyOPPd-9O57LG5lmx7ee_QQ%2Fviewform&d=NgsX4dvaM60oeQzAHgI6lAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=63978a2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfu-KZEnY0rBxEYz1P4uYW-dLuXyOPPd-9O57LG5lmx7ee_QQ/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"f0037e368939a336fac84415481069e03b0d5b25","tid":940674,"uid":76587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T06:26:55.000Z","msg":"入嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140a6705f3a05de13c05db13830d577f24f06384","tid":940674,"uid":76587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T07:30:13.000Z","msg":"好想同大家瘋狂傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c33dd81d810382b55094b9793f8ed47ca9cac3c","tid":940674,"uid":76587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T10:20:54.000Z","msg":"繼續招人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16df32c0f12905fbb65db1b8d82a3d167cf09afb","tid":940674,"uid":76587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:09:50.000Z","msg":"個group新開冇耐咋 <br />\n唔使怕會小圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6e353b8800d992f3dd7f983b0de90133b47900","tid":940674,"uid":76587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T17:57:50.000Z","msg":"夠鐘入谷啦大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ecfec46eec31bc5173f294c6afe9d897277c50","tid":940674,"uid":76587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T01:06:44.000Z","msg":"差你咋！！！唔好諗，快啲入嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji